#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. Rule"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Patirūpasutta"
msgstr "14. Appropriate"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.14:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati ekasālāyaṃ brāhmaṇagāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Kosalans near the "
"brahmin village of Ekasālā."

msgctxt "sn4.14:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time the Buddha was teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large "
"assembly of laypeople."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.248"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.14:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho mārassa pāpimato etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Māra thought:"

msgctxt "sn4.14:2.2"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti."
msgstr ""
"“The ascetic Gotama is teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly of "
"laypeople."

msgctxt "sn4.14:2.3"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ vicakkhukammāyā”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I go and pull the wool over their eyes?”"

msgctxt "sn4.14:2.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.1"
msgid "“Netaṃ tava patirūpaṃ,"
msgstr "“It’s not appropriate for you"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.2"
msgid "yadaññamanusāsasi;"
msgstr "to instruct others."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.3"
msgid "Anurodhavirodhesu,"
msgstr "As you engage in this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.4"
msgid "mā sajjittho tadācaran”ti."
msgstr "don’t get caught up in favoring and opposing.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.1"
msgid "“Hitānukampī sambuddho,"
msgstr "“The Buddha instructs others"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.2"
msgid "yadaññamanusāsati;"
msgstr "out of compassion for their welfare."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.3"
msgid "Anurodhavirodhehi,"
msgstr "The Realized One is liberated"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.4"
msgid "vippamutto tathāgato”ti."
msgstr "from favoring and opposing.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.14:5.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī "
"dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!”"
" miserable and sad, vanished right there."
